{"tid":336861,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"喺屋企得我一個收唔到wifi","createTime":"2017-07-26T18:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T15:11:53.000Z","uid":126137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03fb584da59a8fcffe479036e9a1317a96c32401","tid":336861,"uid":126137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"我自己手機為IPhone 6 唔知點解近兩、三個月我一入房就收唔到屋企wifi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係喺同一間房嘅話 <br />\n屋企部iPad pro 、啊媽部IPhone 7同我家姐部IPhone 6 plus就收得好清楚 有三格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反我有時係完全search唔到屋企個wifi <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明早幾個月仲好地地可以連到<br />\n屋企又無換個router <br />\n有無硬件台嘅巴絲可以幫下我解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nreset router 又得唔得？<br />\nBetween 我上個月去日本係酒店房都收唔到酒店wifi 但同行朋友(IPhone 7)又收到<br />\n去過Apple check又話我個接受wifi功能無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab7db911d2c9c3066d995e6549f008f94bf6836","tid":336861,"uid":112915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"换機或者買個wifi repeater 放房"},{"pid":"7c26c3225bdc1726afaa9c305d2b4d5f76dbf861","tid":336861,"uid":130706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T22:19:32.000Z","msg":"平平地買個home plug / wifi range extender <br />\n自私插係自己間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  普通上網睇片 兩三舊水有找"},{"pid":"776191de3f0ad62cbbab2096705844def533cc9f","tid":336861,"uid":26165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T22:48:35.000Z","msg":"頂我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係好彩先收到一格<br />\n但去人地屋企收到爆哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa192a71a85052b88a85